(34, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:09', '2021-07-16 16:56:09', 'Your customers will love the ease of opening an automatic baton with just the touch of a button with the 21\" EZ Close Twist Lock Expandable Steel Baton. And now, with the EZ close, retracting the baton is effortless. Previous versions of this baton would lock in place once extended and required banging it on the ground with a lot of force to get it to close. The new EZ Close Automatic Expandable Baton does lock in the extended position when you twist the baton, and it allows you to close the baton by just pushing it in with the palm of your hand.\nWhen you need to protect yourself, each second counts. That’s why you should count on the new 21\" EZ Close Twist Lock Expandable Steel Baton. When they want to use less-than-lethal force, police officers and security guards often reach for their automatic metal baton; now civilians can too.\nThis baton expands from 8.5” to 21” with the touch of a button. When ready to close the baton you simply push the tip against the palm of your hand to retract it.\nFEATURES\n\n Superior Design: This high-quality, 8.5-inch steel baton expands to 21 inches.\nTwist Lock: safety feature to guarantee baton locks in place while extended.\nFast Action: Extends in a fraction of a second at just the touch of a button.\nEZ Close: Closes with only a slight push from the palm of your hand.\nRubberized: The rubber handle helps you maintain a firm grip.\nHolster with Belt Loop: Heavy-duty nylon holster for convenient carrying and quick access.\nWarranty: 1 Year\n\nCONTENTS\n\n21\" EZ Close Twist Lock Expandable Steel Baton\nHigh-quality holster with belt loop\n', '21\" EZ Close Twist Lock Expandable Steel Baton', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '21-ez-close-twist-lock-expandable-steel-baton', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:09', '2021-07-16 16:56:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/21-ez-close-twist-lock-expandable-steel-baton/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
