(42, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:12', '2021-07-16 16:56:12', 'Designed for the TASER Pulse/Pulse+, the Appendix Carry holster was created to be worn comfortably on the front side of the body, and can also be positioned to be worn in the cross draw position. The Appendix Carry holster features a CrossBreed® hand-molded pocket for a perfect fit and is a great option for a concealable and comfortable holster.\nThe Appendix Carry Right-handed Holster is designed by CrossBreed for the TASER Pulse/Pulse+ and has no cant so it can be worn on the front side of the body. The Appendix Carry holster features a CrossBreed hand-molded pocket for a perfect fit. We ensure the Appendix Carry is your answer for anyone who wants to carry a firearm in a front position. The Appendix Carry Holster can also be positioned to be worn in the cross draw position.\nFEATURES\nHand-Molded Kydex Shell: Creating the perfect retention and fit for your firearm\nSlim Profile: For additional comfort and flexibility\nHand-Selected Leather Backer: For perfect conformity to your body featuring a soft leather backing\nSteel Snaplok Clip: For longevity and retention to your gun belt\nAdjustable Cant: Allows you to carry in multiple positions\nTuckable Design: For maximum concealment while still tucking in your shirt.\nLifetime Warranty\nCONTENTS\nAppendix Carry Right-handed Holster', 'Appendix Carry Right-handed Holster', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'appendix-carry-right-handed-holster', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:12', '2021-07-16 16:56:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/appendix-carry-right-handed-holster/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
