(49, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:16', '2021-07-16 16:56:16', 'Preloaded and ready to shoot, the COMPACT™ is designed to be convenient and quickly accessible. Using the same technology as our other launchers, this slim design still packs a powerful punch. Weighing a little over 2 ounces, it can be easily stashed in your coat pocket, purse or bookbag, allowing you to add safety and protection to your everyday routine.\nThe COMPACT™ is a powerful PepperBall launcher that can be carried in your pocket. Preloaded and ready to shoot, the COMPACT™ is designed to be convenient and quickly accessible. With a launch distance of up to 30 feet, the COMPACT™ reaches 3X the range of leading personal-sized pepper sprays.Similar to our other Pepperball launchers, the COMPACT™ fires a projectile filled with pepper irritant. Upon impact, the pepperball bursts to release a potent pepper cloud that will quickly and effectively incapacitate a threat.\n*Reload Kit Sold Separately.\nSPECS\n\n\n\n\nSize\n6.9” L x 0.7” W x 1.65” H\n\n\nWeight\n2.5 OZ\n\n\n\nMaximum Launch Distance\n30 Feet\n\n\n\nCapacity\n1 Round\n\n\nAir Source\nN2 Gas Under Pressure\n\n\nRecommended Operation Temperature\n20℉ to 125℉\n\n\nKinetic Impact\n7-14 Joules of Energy\n\n\n\n\n*For use with PepperBall® round projectiles only\nCONTENTS\n\n1 Live SD PepperBall® Projectile \n1 N2 Cartridges\n\n \n\n', 'COMPACT™', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'compact', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:16', '2021-07-16 16:56:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/compact/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
