(53, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:18', '2021-07-16 16:56:18', 'Simply place the Door Stop Alarm behind any door. If an intruder attempts to open the door, the wedge-shaped design will prevent it from opening and activate a 120 dB alarm. The alarm will scare off the would-be intruder and alert you to the attempted entry. The on/off switch will prevent the unit from accidentally sounding.\nFEATURES\n\n120 dB Alarm\n3 sensitivity modes: high, medium, low\nON/OFF switch\nGreat for Home or Travel\nDimensions: 5 ½\" x 2\" x 1 ½\"\n1-year Warranty\n\nREQUIRES\n\nOne 9 volt battery\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Door Stop Alarm', 'Door Stop Alarm', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'door-stop-alarm', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:18', '2021-07-16 16:56:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/door-stop-alarm/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(54, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:19', '2021-07-16 16:56:19', 'The Streetwise Driveway Alert Wireless Notification System will alert you if a car or person enters or exits your driveway. Simply place the transmitter near the entrance to your driveway and the receiver inside your home up to 400 feet away from the transmitter. A person or car passing within 26 feet of the transmitter will cause the receiver to sound either an alarm or a pleasant chime. The transmitter can also be placed by your front door to alert you if small children (or big children at night!) try to leave the house. Business owners can be alerted when customers enter the store while they are working in the back. The adjustable volume ensures you will never miss a customer.\nFEATURES\n Wireless Technology: Simple installation with no holes to dig or wires to run. Just place the transmitter within 400 feet of the receiver.\nWide Detection Range: The transmitter is weatherproof and detects motion from up to 26” away at an angle of 110 degrees.\nSelect your Alert: You can choose a chime or one of 4 alarm sounds\nCompact Size: The transmitter measures 3.75\" x 1\" x 2.5.\" The receiver measures 5.5\" x 1.5\" x 3.5.\"\nPortable: Move to different areas of your property or take with you when traveling.\nWarranty: One year.\n\nREQUIREMENTS\n The receiver requires: three C batteries or a 5-volt adapter (not included)\nTransmitter requires: three AAA batteries (not included)\n\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Driveway Alert (Transmitter and Receiver)\nMounting screws\nInstructions\n\n ', 'Driveway Alert Wireless Notification System', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'driveway-alert-wireless-notification-system', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:19', '2021-07-16 16:56:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/driveway-alert-wireless-notification-system/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
