dpress/product/electra-conceal-carry-handbag/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(56, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:20', '2021-07-16 16:56:20', 'This is no ordinary Backpack. The Emoji Bulletproof Backpack weighs just a pound more than a normal backpack, but it takes a ton of weight off your shoulders knowing your child will be safe at school! It’s like having a bodyguard with your child all the time. There are many high-quality bookbags on the market today but, unlike other bags, the Emoji™ bookbag is bulletproof! You will have peace of mind knowing that it offers protection from nearly all handgun rounds (including a .44 Magnum) as well as sharp or pointed weapons.\nFEATURES\n\nTested to NIJ level 3A bulletproof standards\nCapable of stopping nearly all handgun rounds (even 9mm and .44 Magnum!)\nThe highest level of protection currently available for lightweight (soft) armor\n3.5” x 12“ x 16.5” internal dimensions\n8” x 7” external zippered pocket with three slots for pens/keys/phones/etc.\n8.5” x 5” zippered pocket with rubber zipper pull\nWeighs only 2.75 lbs.\n\nCONTENTS\nStreetwise Emoji™ Bulletproof Backpack ORANGE\nINVENTORY STATUS\nLimited quantities are available. Please call for details.', 'Emoji Bulletproof Backpack', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'emoji-bulletproof-backpack', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:20', '2021-07-16 16:56:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/emoji-bulletproof-backpack/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(57, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:20', '2021-07-16 16:56:20', 'Streetwise Security Products is proud to introduce the “bo on the go”! With a quick twist, the Streetwise Expandable 4\' Bo Staff expands from 21 inches to over 4 feet long (51 inches)! Whether you are using it for self-defense or martial arts training this unique Bo Staff is certain to get the job done! For versatility, we have also included two end caps which allow you to create two 26 inch batons by simply detaching the batons from the center connector and adding the end caps. Have a look at the first video below where a customer compares our new unit to one he manufactures and retails for $129.00. You will see our Bo Staff cut through a watermelon like a warm knife through butter!\nFEATURES \nExpands to 51 inches and locks into place with just a quick twist Can be used as an expandable 51 inch Bo Staff or two 26 inch batons Includes two end caps that are needed when using as individual batons Long reach keeps you a safe distance away from your attacker Rubberized diamond design ensures a firm grip Great for training or self-defense Made from military-grade aluminum alloy Bo staff length collapsed 21” Bo staff length expanded 51”\nCONTENTS\n\n2x Streetwise 26\" Expandable Steel Baton\n1x Connection to form the 51” Bo staff\n2x End Caps for the individual batons\n\n \n \n', 'Expandable 4\' Bo Staff', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'expandable-4-bo-staff', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:20', '2021-07-16 16:56:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/expandable-4-bo-staff/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(58, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:21', '2021-07-16 16:56:21', 'The TASER Extended Digital Power Magazine (XDPM) is compatible with the TASER X26C. The Extended system allows for an extra cartridge to be clipped into the bottom of the unit, providing quick and easy access to reload your TASER X26C.\nFEATURES\n\n\nExtended systems stores an extra cartridge \n100 10-second firings \n\nDEVICE COMPATIBILITY\n\nX26C\n\nDIMENSIONS\n\n Height: 3.2 inches (8.1 cm)\nLength (w/o Cartridge): 6.0 inches (15.2 cm)\nLength (w/ Cartridge): 7.3 inches (18.5 cm)\nWidth: 1.3 inches (3.3 cm)\nWeight (w/o Cartridge): 7.2 oz (204 g)\n\nCONTENTS\nTaser X26C XDPM-Extended DPM-Holds Extra Cartridge\nPlease note that environmental conditions, such as extreme heat or cold, can cause variations in battery life. This is not a rechargeable battery.\n', 'Extended Digital Power Magazine (XDPM)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'extended-digital-power-magazine-xdpm', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:21', '2021-07-16 16:56:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/extended-digital-power-magazine-xdpm/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
