(60, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:22', '2021-07-16 16:56:22', 'This set of Fake Security Beam - Imitation Infrared Detector imitates the photoelectric sensors that are used in most high-end security systems today. Criminals know that these sensors are placed across from each other to cause an invisible beam to pass between them and if that beam is broken the alarm system is triggered. The criminal will think that you have a high- end security system installed and go in search of an easier target.\nFEATURES\n\nThese fake sensors have red flashing lights on the front to draw the attention of anyone who steps foot on your property.\nLook like real sensors\nEasy Mounting\nWarranty: 90 days\n\nREQUIRES\nEach unit requires 2 AA batteries (4 total)\nCONTENTS\n\nFake Security Beam- Imitation Infrared Detector\nIncludes wall and pole mounting hardware.\n\nINVENTORY STATUS\nA limited quantity is available. Please call for details.*\n*The price of this item has been drastically reduced since there are limited quantities available. Once our remaining stock is depleted this item will be discontinued.', 'Fake Security Beam - Imitation Infrared Detector', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'fake-security-beam-imitation-infrared-detector', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:22', '2021-07-16 16:56:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/fake-security-beam-imitation-infrared-detector/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(61, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:23', '2021-07-16 16:56:23', 'We now offer an attractive and eye-catching Fire Gone 24 Can Floor Display. This display makes an excellent POP display for stores, flea markets, or any retail outlet.\nFire Gone is a wonderful alternative to traditional fire extinguishers because the discharge time is much faster which helps reduce the loss of life and property. It is a trigger-style aerosol that, once activated, releases a powerful foam blanket on the ignited material to suppress the fire. Fire Gone utilizes a formula that has been researched and developed for over 20 years, resulting in a revolutionary way to extinguish small fires safely and rapidly.\nHOW DOES IT WORK?\nFire Gone is specially formulated to form a vapor suppressing aqueous film on hydrocarbon type fuels or a polymeric membrane on polar solvent/water miscible type fuels. The molecules then form a vapor suppressing seal for rapid control of fire while blocking the release of further vapor fuel. Fire Gone Formulation encapsulates the fire itself while forming a high-quality foam blanket that floats on the outside of the ignited material starving it of oxygen. Water contained in this foam blanket cools the ignited material while continuously forming more foam barriers.\nFEATURES\n\n Durable Display: This display holds 24 of the Fire Gone Units with no problem!\nEye Catching: With the colorful top and the bright red bottom of this display, customers are sure to see it!\nFire Gone has been tested by the internationally recognized Bureau Veritas Consumer Product Services Inc., to be effective on: Class A - Wood, Straw, Hay, Cotton, Tires, Fabric, Paper. Class B - Gasoline/Diesel, Fuels. Class C - Electrical Equipment Fires. Class K - Grease, Cooking Oils, Animal Fats, Vegetable Fats\nSafety Feature: Comes with a black tab so the unit doesn’t discharge if something hits it accidentally.\nConvenient Size: Being only 10” high and 3” round, this unit is less than half the size of your average fire extinguisher making it perfect to store anywhere!\nEasy Clean-Up: Simply wipe the area with a damp cloth after the fire has died out. Leaves no messy residue behind. Will not damage boat or auto parts.\nEnvironmentally Safe: Fire Gone is environmentally safe and biodegradable. Fire Gone is non-toxic and does not use harsh synthetic chemicals or acids. Additionally, Fire Gone Fire Extinguisher is noncorrosive.\n\nCONTENTS\n\nDisplay\n24 Fire Gone 16oz Cans\n\nINVENTORY STATUS\nLimited quantity is available at this blowout price. Please call for available quantities and the “take all” price.', 'Fire Gone 24 Can Floor Display', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'fire-gone-24-can-floor-display', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:23', '2021-07-16 16:56:23', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/fire-gone-24-can-floor-display/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
