(74, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:29', '2021-07-16 16:56:29', 'The Iris Conceal Carry Handbag\'s casual and compact design makes Iris one of the most comfortable crossbody bags that you can have! It has three spacious pockets for all of your necessary items. Includes a cell phone pocket as well as a rear pocket for your small items. Made from vegan leather, this handbag is extremely lightweight and can be used as either a clutch or crossbody. The removable shoulder strap is reinforced with a cut-resistant metal wire for added security. The concealed carry pocket is located in the center of the bag and has access from either the left or right side as well as the top.\nFEATURES\n Handbag Dimensions: 11\" x 8\" x 4\"\nConcealment Compartment: 7.5\" x 10\" x 5.5\"\nAmbidextrous Access: discreet zippers are located on both sides of the compartment, so firearms can be quickly accessed by both right and left-handed shooters.\nVelcro Holster: Keeps the gun secured in a safe position so you can access it quickly in an emergency.\nMultiple Pockets: two external zippered pockets and one zippered pouch on the inside. There are also two small slot pouches inside for smaller objects.\nWorry-free Replacement*: should you ever shoot through the handbag in self-defense, send us a copy of the police report, and we\'ll send you a free replacement bag. \nTheft-resistant Shoulder Strap and Handles: An anti-cut wire is located inside the handles to prevent a thief from cutting them and stealing the purse.\nWarranty: Limited Lifetime\n\nCONTENTS\n\nCameleon Iris Handbag\nVelcro Gun Holster\nRemovable Shoulder Strap\n\nDISCLAIMER\nLawful concealed carry of a personal firearm is subject to legislation at both the State and Federal level. Any person concealing a firearm without the license or lawful right to do so subjects themselves to the appropriate legal repercussions.\n*IMPORTANT: If you ever need to shoot through the handbag to protect yourself you can send us a copy of the police report, and we will send you a free replacement bag.', 'Iris Conceal Carry Handbag', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'iris-conceal-carry-handbag', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:29', '2021-07-16 16:56:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/iris-conceal-carry-handbag/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(75, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:29', '2021-07-16 16:56:29', 'The JUSTinCASE 17,000,000* Stun Gun Power Bank looks like a regular phone case wallet, but it\'s so much more:\nJust in case you\'re attacked - it\'s a Stun Gun!\nJust in case your phone is dead - it\'s a Power Bank!\nJust in case you need a light at night - it\'s a Flashlight!\nJust in case you need to check yourself or check behind you - it\'s a Mirror!\nThe JUSTinCASE 17,000,000* Stun Gun Power Bank provides Power, Protection, and Light - Just in Case, you need it!\nFEATURES\n\nTwo ID/credit card slots\nMagnetic clasp\nBelt/Purse clip rotates 90 degrees\n1800mAH Power Bank with USB charging port to charge your phone or another device on the go\nBright LED flashlight\nPower indicator light\nStun Gun\n\nCONTENTS\n\nJUSTinCASE 17,000,000* Stun Gun Power Bank\nUSB charging cable\nInstructions\n\n*Actual Voltage output is difficult to measure and verify, but this unit compares to other brands that claim to be 17,000,000 or more volts.', 'JUSTinCASE 17,000,000* Stun Gun Power Bank', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'justincase-17000000-stun-gun-power-bank', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:29', '2021-07-16 16:56:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/justincase-17000000-stun-gun-power-bank/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
