(77, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:30', '2021-07-16 16:56:30', 'In the midst of the rising tide of violent crime, you can trust the “Lady Life Guard” to protect you! The Lady Life Guard 6,500,000* Stun Gun is loaded with great features and packs a powerful punch! Its ergonomic design makes it a favorite among women because they can wrap their hands completely around the rubberized unit for a firm grip that feels natural in your hand. It features a bright LED light, disable pin, slide-out charging plugs, and a strong stun.\nImportant: Please don’t confuse our Streetwise Lady Life Guard 6500 with other models that look similar. Some of the other models are plastic and have a very weak electrical charge and light. Once you experience how good our rubberized unit feels in your hand and compare the electrical charge you will be shocked by the difference!\nThe Lady Life Guard helps women in 2 ways: first as a self-defense device with great features and second because a portion of the proceeds is used to help fight breast cancer.\nFEATURES\n Powerful Stun: Just test firing this unit into the air is often enough to stop an attacker. As the bright electric current pulsates across the top, it creates an intimidating electrical sound. An attacker with any sense will be stopped in his tracks. If the sight and sound don\'t stop him, a jolt from this unit certainly will.\nErgonomic Design: Unlike many other models that feel awkward and bulky, this ergonomic design provides you with a comfortable, firm grip that feels natural in your hand. This can give you greater confidence in your ability to defend yourself even under stressful situations. Measures: 4 1/4” Long, 1 5/8” Wide, 1” Deep\nBuilt-in Charger: The slide-out plug on the side of the unit allows for easy charging. There are no cords to keep up with; simply plug into a standard wall outlet.\nSafety Switch: To prevent accidental discharge, three levels of safety have been built-in.\nRubberized Armor Coating: Protects the unit and ensures a firm grip.\nDisable Pin: Prevents an attacker from taking this stun gun away and using it on you. A strap worn around the wrist attaches to a disable pin on the bottom of the unit. If the stun gun is taken from you, the pin will pull out, preventing it from working. For those with small children removing the pin turns the unit into an ordinary flashlight. You can store the pin and wrist strap separately to keep it safe from your little ones.\nBright LED Light: Provides a convenient source of light whenever you need it and eliminates the need to carry a heavy, bulky flashlight.\nHolster Included: Although this model is slim enough to carry in your pocket or purse, a holster with belt loop is included.\nPink ribbon series: A portion of the proceeds from the sale of this product goes to fight breast cancer\nLifetime Warranty: Made of the highest quality components and comes with a lifetime warranty.\n\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Life Guard Stun Gun- Pink\nDisable Pin\nHolster\nInstruction Manual\n\nINVENTORY STATUS\nLimited quantity is available at this blowout price. Please call for available quantities and the “take all” price.\n*Actual Voltage output is difficult to measure and verify, but this unit compares to other brands that claim to be 6,500,000 or more volts.\n ', 'Lady Life Guard 6,500,000* Stun Gun', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lady-life-guard-6500000-stun-gun', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:30', '2021-07-16 16:56:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/lady-life-guard-6500000-stun-gun/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
