(80, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:32', '2021-07-16 16:56:32', 'Originally designed for the military, the LifeLite Defense Launcher integrates a bright LED flashlight with a powerful PepperBall launcher to offer covert protection in plain sight. Equipped with a built-in laser guide allowing you to hit a target with ease. Store it in your bedside table or glove compartment, and you have peace of mind whether you are at home or on the go.\nThe PepperBall® LifeLite™ combines a bright, LED flashlight with a launcher to offer covert protection in plain sight. Designed to launch non-lethal PepperBall® projectiles from as far as 60 feet away, the built-in laser guide helps the user find and hit the target with ease, and a safety switch ensures that LifeLite™ won’t fire until you want it to. \nFEATURES\n\nLaser Guide\nLED Flashlight\nCO2 Load Chamber\nLaunch Chamber\nAmbidextrous Safety\nTrigger\nPush Button - Flashlight operation\nProjectile Load Chamber - 5 round capacity\n\n\nSPECIFICATIONS\n\n\n\n\n\nSize\n11-1/4\" L x 2-5/16\" W x 2-9/16\" H\n\n\nWeight\n1.75 lbs\n\n\nLumen\n350\n\n\nMaximum Launch Distance\n60 ft\n\n\nCapacity\n5 Rounds\n\n\nAir Source\nCO2\n\n\n\nRecommended Operation Temperature\n20℉ to 125℉\n\n\n\n\n*For use with PepperBall® round projectiles only*CO2 performance diminishes below 32℉\nCONTENTS\n\n5 Live SD™ PepperBall® Projectiles \n10 Inert Practice Projectiles\n3 CO2 Cartridges\n2 CR123 Batteries\nLanyard\n', 'LifeLite Defense Launcher', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lifelite-defense-launcher', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:32', '2021-07-16 16:56:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/lifelite-defense-launcher/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(81, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:32', '2021-07-16 16:56:32', 'The LifeLite Holster/Carrying Case is a Black Nylon Holster with belt clip for carrying the LifeLite™ Launcher', 'LifeLite Holster/Carrying Case', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lifelite-holster-carrying-case', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:32', '2021-07-16 16:56:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/lifelite-holster-carrying-case/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(82, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:33', '2021-07-16 16:56:33', 'PROTECTION WHEN YOU NEED IT\nThe right solution for a non-lethal approach to your personal protection and to protect your family when their safety is threatened. \nDOG WALKING | RV TRAVEL | COMMERCIAL TRUCKINGPERSONAL SAFETY | CAMPING | HOME DEFENSE | BOATING\n\nThe PepperBall LifeLite Mobile Defense Launcher offers the right solution for a non-lethal approach to your personal protection and to protect your family when their safety is threatened.\nBuilt on the success of the first generation, LifeLite Mobile is designed to be more portable and convenient to transport or carry. Equipped with a dual-LED flashlight and built-in PepperBall launcher, LifeLite Mobile offers covert protection in plain sight. Designed to launch PepperBall projectiles from as far as 40 feet away, the built-in light guide helps the user find and hit the target with ease.\nThe PepperBall LifeLite Mobile is the next step in non-lethal self-defense. It integrates a highly effective pepper ball launcher into a common everyday flashlight. Using CO2 power, the LifeLite can launch a powerful pepper ball that is filled with a fine pepper powder up to 40 feet. This provides you a greater amount of space than any other non-lethal self-defense weapon. Furthermore, the pepper ball does not need to make contact with an attacker to be effective. Once it hits their vicinity, the pepper irritant disperses within a 12-foot radius and easily enters their nose, mouth, and eyes. The dust cloud created by a PepperBall is made of a proprietary, pharmaceutical-grade PAVA pepper powder that causes an immediate burning and itching sensation in the eyes, nose, throat, and chest, which allows you time to escape and get help. This irritating feeling lasts for up to 15 minutes. There is also a built-in laser sight that provides accurate aiming, so you can be sure to hit your target and make it to safety. On top of that, the LifeLite is a powerful 350-lumen flashlight that illuminates the darkest of areas and is great for everyday uses as well, making it the perfect all-in-one device for any safety-minded individual.\nFEATURES\n\nCombines a flashlight and PepperBall launcher into a single device\nSemi-automatic firing system\nBright 350-lumen flashlight\nIntegrated laser sight for rapid target acquisition.\nOptional rechargeable battery &amp; charger available\nFires up to 40 feet\nThree-round capacity\nOne Year Warranty\n\nCONTENTS\n\n1 LifeLite Mobile Launcher\n6 Live SD PepperBall Projectiles\n12 Inert Practice Projectiles\n3 CO2 Cartridges\n', 'LifeLite Mobile Defense Launcher', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lifelite-mobile-defense-launcher', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:33', '2021-07-16 16:56:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/lifelite-mobile-defense-launcher/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
