(100, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:42', '2021-07-16 16:56:42', 'The Outdoor 8.5\" Tactical Rescue Knife is a nice brawny knife for everyday carry. The coated stainless steel blade will see you through almost any task you throw at it - military, tactical, rescue, or outdoors. Opens super quick with just a finger. Measures 5\" closed, 8.5\" open. Easy to carry - slip it in your pocket or clip it to your pocket or belt with the sturdy belt clip.\nAs a member of the American Knife and Tool Institute (AKTI), we are committed to ensuring that Americans will always be able to make, buy, sell, carry, and use the knife and edged tool of their choice with confidence. To learn more see AKTI.org\nFEATURES\n\n5\" ABS Handle\n3.5\" Stainless Steel Blade\nBelt Clip\nAssisted Open\nLiner Lock\n90-Day Warranty\n\nCONTENTS\nOutdoor Tactical Rescue Knife', 'Outdoor 8.5\" Tactical Rescue Knife', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'outdoor-8-5-tactical-rescue-knife', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:42', '2021-07-16 16:56:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/outdoor-8-5-tactical-rescue-knife/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(101, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:42', '2021-07-16 16:56:42', 'Security is now as close as your keys. The Streetwise Panic Keychain Alarm features a fast and simple squeeze and scares operation that allows you to quickly activate the alarm at the same time you grab the unit.\nFEATURES\nPanic Alarm: Simply grab the device and squeeze the sides to sound the alarm. The alarm is loud enough to be heard by anyone nearby.\nLED Light:  LED Light for Nighttime Safety:  Don\'t be afraid to walk alone in the dark. With this bright LED light you will see an attacker before he/she can sneak up on you.\nKeychain Attachment: A person is most likely to be attacked at night while walking to or from their car or home. This compact alarm easily attaches to your keys or clips to your purse or clothing so it\'s always within reach. Many other personal alarms can be difficult to use in a panic situation.\n1-year Warranty\n\nCONTENTS\nStreetwise Panic Keychain Alarm', 'Panic Keychain Alarm', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'panic-keychain-alarm', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:42', '2021-07-16 16:56:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/panic-keychain-alarm/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(102, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:43', '2021-07-16 16:56:43', 'The TASER Performance Power Magazine (PPM) is a lithium energy cell power supply system. \nFEATURES\nX26P: Approximately 500 5-second trigger-initiated firings\nX2: Approximately 250 5-second ARC switch-initiated firings\nDEVICE COMPATIBILITY\n\nX2\nX26P\n\nCONTENTS\n\nTASER Performance Power Magazine (PPM)\nPlease note that environmental conditions, such as extreme heat or cold, can cause variations in battery life. This battery is non-rechargeable.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'Performance Power Magazine (PPM)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'performance-power-magazine-ppm', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:43', '2021-07-16 16:56:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/performance-power-magazine-ppm/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(103, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:43', '2021-07-16 16:56:43', 'The Perfume Protector 17,000,000* Stun Gun is a compact yet powerful stun gun that is designed for the man you want to keep out of your life. It looks just like a perfume spray bottle, so it is small enough to carry in your pocket or purse. But don\'t let its small size fool you - it may be discrete and easy to conceal, but it is capable of bringing an attacker to his knees.\nThe Streetwise stun gun is a self-defense device that disrupts the messages the brain sends to the voluntary muscles. Simply touching an attacker with a stun gun for three to five seconds will deliver a high voltage shock causing loss of balance and muscle control, confusion, and disorientation, bringing him to his knees and making him incapable of further aggressive activity. Full recovery takes about five to ten minutes and there is no permanent harm.\nFEATURES\n Rechargeable: Recharge cord (included) plugs into a standard wall outlet to save you money on batteries.\nBright LED Flashlight: Ideal for night-time safety.\nDiscrete Protection: Provides you with the element of surprise if you need to defend yourself.\nSafety Cap: To prevent accidental discharge, a safety cap covers the stun button.\nLifetime Warranty: Streetwise Stun Guns are one of the highest quality brands available and come with a lifetime warranty.\n\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Perfume Protector 17,000,000* Stun Gun\nSafety Cap\nInstruction Manual\nWall Charger\n\n*Actual Voltage output is difficult to measure and verify, but this unit compares to other brands that claim to be 17,000,000 or more volts.', 'Perfume Protector 17,000,000* Stun Gun', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'perfume-protector-17000000-stun-gun', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:43', '2021-07-16 16:56:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/perfume-protector-17000000-stun-gun/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(104, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:44', '2021-07-16 16:56:44', 'Keep you or your important things safe with the Personal Door Protection Alarm w/Light!\nFEATURES\nPersonal Alarm: carry it in a purse or pocket or attach it to your belt using the clip on the back of the alarm. In an emergency, pulling the cord will activate the 130 DB alarm and flashing light. The alarm and light will draw attention to the situation, scare off a would-be attacker, and summon help.\nPurse/Briefcase/Backpack Alarm: when the cord is clipped to your belt or wrapped around your wrist and the alarm is placed inside your purse, briefcase, or backpack the alarm will sound if someone attempts to take it from you.\nDoor or Window Alarm: the personal alarm can instantly be converted into a door or window alarm using the included door clip accessory. Opening the protected door or window will activate the alarm and flashing light to alert you to the attempted entry.\nLaptop Computer Alarm: the door clip accessory mentioned above can also be used to protect a laptop computer or other valuable property. Once the door clip accessory is placed underneath your property, anyone picking up that object will activate the alarm and flashing light.\nCompact design: Unbreakable plastic shell and small size which is great for travel - Measurements are 3\" x 2\" x 1\"\nWarranty: 1 year\nREQUIRES\nOne 9 volt battery (not included)\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Personal/Door Alarm with Light\nInstruction Manual\nPull pin cord with key ring and plastic attachment\nSpring-loaded clip for use on doors, windows, laptop, or other valuables\n', 'Personal Door Protection Alarm w/Light', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'personal-door-protection-alarm-w-light', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:44', '2021-07-16 16:56:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/personal-door-protection-alarm-w-light/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(105, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:44', '2021-07-16 16:56:44', 'The Personal Protection Alarm may be secured to a belt or clothing with the included belt clip or attached to a purse with the included lanyard. When the safety pin is removed, a loud 130-decibel alarm will sound.\nFEATURES\n\nEar-piecing alarm\nWill sound for up to 2 continuous hours.\nCompact size is great for home or travel: With an unbreakable plastic shell and small size\nMeasures 3 inches x 2 and one-eighths inches x 1 and one-eighths inches\nPerfect for keeping yourself and your property safe.\n1-Year Warranty\n\nREQUIRES\nOne 9 volt battery (not included)\nCONTENTS\nStreetwise Personal Alarm with a safety pin with lanyard', 'Personal Protection Alarm', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'personal-protection-alarm', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:44', '2021-07-16 16:56:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/personal-protection-alarm/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(106, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:45', '2021-07-16 16:56:45', 'The Police Force 23 Pepper Spray Flip Top has a very unique safety mechanism. The top flips up and with a push of your finger, the spray is released. This safety lock makes it impossible for the pepper spray to go off when not in use.\nWhen it comes to protecting yourself and your loved ones, how can you really know which pepper spray is the most effective?\nFEATURES\n\nFlip-top Safety Lock\nIndependent Laboratory Heat Rating Certified\n\nDerived from over 5 Million SHU**\n87% Stronger than Competing Brands\nInstantly repels an Attacker\nIncapacitates for up to 45 minutes\nUV Marking Dye\n1.47% Total Capsaicinoids\nWarranty: 1 year for canister and nozzle, until expiration date for pepper spray\n\nINDEPENDENT LAB TESTING\n\nAlthough many brands claim to be the best, we recommend you consider the unbiased results of an independent laboratory* that tests the heat of the pepper once it is sprayed out of the can. The Certified Heat Rating (CHR) measures how hot the pepper spray will be once it comes in contact with your attacker.\nPolice Force 23 Pepper Spray has a CHR of over 230,000 SHU (1.47% Total Capsaicinoids) making it one of the hottest, most effective self-defense sprays on the market. For comparison, the independent laboratory tested competing brands. They found the average heat rating to be 123,000 SHU, making Streetwise 23 over 87% hotter than the competition!\nOur pepper spray is so potent that it can incapacitate an attacker for up to 45 minutes without causing any permanent harm.\nSome brands make exaggerated marketing claims. The only true way to know the actual effectiveness of a pepper spray is to have it tested by an independent laboratory.\nFor us, \"Protecting What Matters Most\" is more than just a slogan. It\'s our commitment to provide you with a top-quality self-defense spray that you can rely on to protect what matters most to you.\nCONTENTS\nPolice Force 23 Pepper Spray Flip Top\n*We have our pepper spray certified by the same independent laboratory (Chromtec LLC) that has been used by pepper spray manufacturers and the US Government for over 40 years. This certificate is available upon request.\n**We add a small amount of pure capsaicin (which is well over 5,000,000 SHU) to boost our CHR to over 230,000.', 'Police Force 23 Pepper Spray Flip Top', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'police-force-23-pepper-spray-flip-top', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:45', '2021-07-16 16:56:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/police-force-23-pepper-spray-flip-top/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
