(108, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:46', '2021-07-16 16:56:46', 'The Streetwise Pro-Tech Bulletproof Tote Bag protects you from the bulletproof plate shown in the video.\nThe Streetwise Pro-Tech Tote is a Bulletproof tote bag with a power bank. It is large enough to carry your 15-inch laptop as well as everything else you need to keep with you for your “on the go” lifestyle. With the included power bank and patent-pending battery interface, you can charge and use your device at the same time. The charging ports are located on the outside of the bag so keeping your phone charged has never been easier. Not only do you no longer have to worry about your devices running out of power, but this lightweight tote bag provides you with peace of mind knowing that you will be protected from nearly all handgun rounds (even 9mm and .44 Magnum) as well as sharp or pointed weapons.\nFEATURES\n\nLevel 3A bulletproof rating from the NIJ (National Institute of Justice)\nCapable of stopping nearly all handgun rounds (even .44 Magnum!)\nThe highest level of protection available for lightweight (soft) armor\nLarge tote bag measures 15.5\" H x 14.5\" W x 5.0\" D\nRemovable, rechargeable 4000 mAh Power Bank\nPatent-pending charging system\nCharging ports are located on the outside\nUp to 25 hours of battery life for your phone / 8 hours for your laptop\n2 large, padded interior compartments to protect your devices\nLaptop compartment with Velcro closure (fits most 15” laptops)\nTwo device or water bottle pockets on the sides\nIncludes a neoprene accessory pouch that holds a standard iPad\nAdjustable and easily removable shoulder strap\nWater and tear-resistant 1000 denier nylon\nIncludes cable to charge the power bank\nTop-quality zipper\nWeighs 4.4 lbs.\n\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Pro-Tech Bulletproof Tote Bag\nNeoprene accessory pouch\nCable to charge the power bank\nShoulder strap\n\nINVENTORY STATUS\nLimited quantities are available. Please call for details.', 'Pro-Tech Bulletproof Tote Bag', ''