(124, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:54', '2021-07-16 16:56:54', 'With the increased popularity and miniaturization of Wi-Fi spy cameras, privacy in hotels is on everyone’s mind. According to a recent article in Forbes magazine entitled, “Why you should start screening for hidden spy cameras when you travel“, concern over SPY cams in hotels and vacation rentals can no longer be dismissed as far-fetched. There has been a steady stream of news stories regarding travelers discovering hidden cameras and items such as smoke detectors, alarm clocks, and chargers, and even shampoo bottles. Last year there was an arrest made after someone illegally live-streamed over 1600 hotel guests. The article went on to state that 6 in 10 Airbnb guests were concerned about the use of hidden cameras in vacation rentals and 1 in 10 guests had actually found hidden cameras in their rental.\nIt is with these alarming statistics in mind that Streetwise Security Products introduces the Spy Spotter Hidden Camera Detector. This new security gadget is simple to use. You simply look through the lens and the flashing red LED lights will spot even pinhole-sized spy cameras inside clocks, lamps, picture frames, and phone chargers, fans, electrical outlets, DVD players, air fresheners, and more. The rechargeable Spy Spotter is the perfect travel companion, once you\'re sure your room or rental is free of spy cameras you can hang it on the door and use the motion detection feature to alert you if someone tries to enter. When traveling to and from your destination this feature can also be used to protect your luggage, laptop, or anything of value. If the object has moved an alarm will sound and red lights will flash, scaring away the thief and alerting you.\nFEATURES\n3 LED Modes: Three different flashing modes to detect all types of cameras. Motion Activated Alarm: Hang the alarm on a doorknob, luggage, or any other item you wish to protect with the included lanyard.\nRechargeable: fast charging with an included USB charging cord.\n30-day warranty: There is a warranty period of one year that covers defects in materials or workmanship.\nCONTENTS\n\n\nStreetwise Spy Spotter Hidden Camera Detector\nUSB Charging Cord\n\nLanyard\n\n', 'Spy Spotter Hidden Camera Detector', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'spy-spotter-hidden-camera-detector', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:54', '2021-07-16 16:56:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/spy-spotter-hidden-camera-detector/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
