(126, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:54', '2021-07-16 16:56:54', 'Just released: the new Sting Ring by Streetwise Security Products is now available in HD! We are excited to announce the Sting Ring HD 18,000,000* Stun Gun! We used a process called Hydro Dipping to create an awesome design that is brand new to the stun gun industry.\nA couple of years ago Streetwise Security Products introduced the Sting Ring Stun Gun. People loved the unique, patented design and it quickly became one of the best-selling stun guns. What separates this unit from all other models on the market today is its concealability- the base fits in the palm of your hand exposing only the ring around your finger. The rounded base feels natural in your hand, and when gripped firmly it\'s nearly impossible for an attacker to take it from you. The Squeeze-N-Stun Technology could save your life by saving you valuable seconds when defending yourself in a panic situation. Rather than having to fumble around looking for the right buttons to push you simply turn off the safety and tighten your grip to activate the unit and stun your attacker!\nAlthough this item can be easily carried in a pocket or purse or concealed in the palm of your hand if you prefer a holster see item PFHCH below under related products.\nThe Sting Ring is one of the most effective and easiest to use stun guns on the market today but, don\'t just take our word for it. Catherine from San Antonio, TX, is a nurse who credits the Sting Ring for saving her two separate times. Once from a robber and once from a vicious dog! This is her amazing story……..\n“I’d like to tell you about my Sting Ring made by Streetwise. I recently purchased 2 for personal safety. I was placed in a position to have to use it twice. First, as I was leaving a local grocery store my purse was grabbed from behind….” (Click the reviews tab above for the rest of the story)\nFEATURES\n US Patent No. US D812,709 S: There is no other stun gun like this in the world. Please contact us for additional information and supporting documents.\nDesigned to Defend: The ease of use, concealability, and strong electric current make this model one of the best new stun gun models on the market today!\nSqueeze-N-Stun Technology: When it comes to protecting yourself, saving seconds can save your life! In a panic situation, the stun gun can be activated quickly and easily by simply squeezing it. This new technology saves you valuable time by not having to fumble around for the right button to push and your tight grip around the unit prevents it from being knocked out of your hand.\nConcealed by Your Hand: The base of the unit is concealed inside your closed fist, leaving only the “Sting Ring” exposed. Your attacker will never know you are carrying a stun gun giving you the element of surprise.\nSmall &amp; Lightweight: Eliminates the need to carry a heavy, bulky self-defense product. Ideal for those exercising outdoors or just walking to and from your car.\nSafety Feature: To prevent accidental discharge, the Sting Ring features a safety switch.\nRechargeable: The recharging cord (included) plugs into a standard wall outlet to save you money on batteries and protect the environment.\nLifetime Warranty: The Sting Ring is made by Streetwise Security Products- the leader in the personal protection industry and features a lifetime warranty.\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Sting Ring HD 18,000,000 Stun Gun\nCharging Cord\nInstructions\n\n*Actual Voltage output is difficult to measure and verify, but this unit compares to other brands that claim to be 18,000,000 or more volts.', 'Sting Ring HD 18,000,000* Stun Gun', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'sting-ring-hd-18000000-stun-gun', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:54', '2021-07-16 16:56:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/sting-ring-hd-18000000-stun-gun/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(127, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:55', '2021-07-16 16:56:55', 'We now offer an attractive and eye-catching countertop display with the Streetwise Security Countertop Display. This makes an excellent POP display for stores, flea markets, or any retail outlet.\nFEATURES\nEye Catching: The Streetwise Countertop Display holds 10 clamshell products of your choice. With black and Yellow graphics and our Police Force Policeman on the front, it\'s definitely an eye-catcher!\nVersatile Space: Remove the clamshell center to put in stun gun packaging or boxes of your choice.\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Countertop Display', 'Streetwise Security Countertop Display', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'streetwise-security-countertop-display', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:55', '2021-07-16 16:56:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/streetwise-security-countertop-display/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(128, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:55', '2021-07-16 16:56:55', 'Combining the usefulness of a high-intensity flashlight with the protection of a stun gun, the StrikeLight is a useful device for everyday civilian self-defense. The TASER StrikeLight stun flashlight makes the perfect addition to your glovebox or a discrete self-protection tool on late-night hikes and neighborhood dog walks. The light’s high-voltage stun both startles and repels attackers, providing you with added comfort and safety.\n\nFEATURES\nPowerful 80 Lumen Flashlight: Powerful 80 Lumen Flashlight – helps you find your way (or your keys).\nArc Warning: Deter intruders or let a would-be attacker know you mean business with the touch of a button.\nStun Capability: Keep your attackers at bay when a close interaction is unavoidable with the Strikelight’s contact stun feature. \nProtect What Matters: We believe that less-lethal self-defense is better self-defense. Protect what matters with fewer consequences and more peace of mind. State regulations vary, so consider your state before purchasing.\nBuilt to Last: Pick up the TASER StrikeLight and you\'ll realize immediately it was built to last. The housing is made from Covestro\'s PC-ABS blend (known for its incredible durability) ensuring it can be carried wherever you go.\nAdaptable Device: The TASER StrikeLight provides an extra layer of personal protection in a limitless variety of uses. Keep it in your glovebox, take it on a walk, or put it in your backpack the next time you go on mass transit or beyond the city limits.\nCONTENTS\n\nTaser StrikeLight Device\nRechargeable Battery\nWall Charger\nWrist-Strap for Secure Carrying\n', 'StrikeLight', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'strikelight', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:55', '2021-07-16 16:56:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/strikelight/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(129, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:56', '2021-07-16 16:56:56', 'The Stunbrella 32,000,000* Stun Flashlight designed by Streetwise Security Products is the most innovative concealed stun gun to come on the market in several years. This “umbrella” will not protect you from the rain but it will protect you from an attacker by \"raining down\" a powerful charge on any bad guy that gets too close! This patented 10-inch stun gun looks like an ordinary folded umbrella. Nowadays umbrellas are used both to protect people from the rain and the sun’s harmful UV rays so it is commonplace to see people carrying them in all kinds of weather. The Stunbrella can be carried discreetly in your hand, a purse or backpack, or stored in the car so it will always be within arm\'s reach and easily accessible at the first sign of trouble.\nConcealed stun guns give you the element of surprise that is often needed to gain an advantage over your attacker. By the time they realize you are armed with a powerful stun gun they will be on the ground wondering what happened! Additionally, the 10-inch long Stunbrella gives you an extended reach that keeps the distance between you and your attacker.\nThe stun gun works through the protective sleeve so the only time you need to remove it is at night when you want to use the bright flashlight.\nFEATURES\n US Patent No. US D879,909 S: There is no other stun gun like this in the world. Please contact us for additional information and supporting documents.\nSqueeze to Stun: the Stun Activation Button is built into the grip, making the Stunbrella easy to use\nLightweight: weighs less than a comparable sized real umbrella!\nLong Reach: no need to get too close to an attacker\nSafety Switch: thumb-controlled safety switch prevents accidental discharge\nContoured Handle: the indented handle adds to the realism and delivers a comfortable grip\nWrist Strap: you wouldn\'t want to drop your umbrella in a puddle, and you sure don\'t want to drop your Stunbrella when you need it!\nBright LED Light: the flashlight on the Stunbrella will illuminate your path at night and you can shine it in an assailant\'s eyes!\nRechargeable Battery: keep the Stunbrella charged by plugging it into a standard outlet\n\nCONTENTS\n\nStreetwise Stunbrella 32,000,000* Stun Flashlight BLACK\nCharging Cable\nInstructions\n\n*Actual voltage output is difficult to measure and verify, but this unit compares to other brands that claim to be 32,000,000 or more volts.', 'Stunbrella 32,000,000* Stun Flashlight', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'stunbrella-32000000-stun-flashlight', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:56', '2021-07-16 16:56:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/stunbrella-32000000-stun-flashlight/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(130, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:56', '2021-07-16 16:56:56', 'JOLT, the power of a lightning bolt!\nIf you’re looking for high quality, economically priced stun gun, the patented JOLT Tactical 75,000,000* Stun Flashlight is for you. It is made of military-grade aluminum alloy and packs the stun and flashlight power of larger devices into a unit less than six inches long!\nFEATURES\n US Design Patent No. US D736,975 S: Please contact us for additional information and supporting documents.\nPowerful Protection: When you compare this compact tactical stun flashlight to other models on the market you will be SHOCKED by how much stronger this model is.\nShock Proof Exterior: Military Grade aluminum alloy protects it from damage so it can always be ready to protect you\nNo-Slip Grip: Etched diamond texture in the handle ensures a firm grip\nBright Light: Not only will the flashlight safely illuminate the entire area at night, but it can also help protect you. When shined in the eyes of an attacker, the ultra-bright light can have a temporary blinding effect making it easy for you to immobilize them with the stun gun. Other brands state the brightness of this light as 160 to 200 lumens\nSafety Features: To prevent accidental discharge, three levels of safety have been built-in\nRechargeable: Recharge cord (included) plugs into a standard wall outlet to save you money on batteries\nHolster and Wrist Strap Included: To make this unit easy to carry, the unit includes a wrist strap and nylon holster with belt loop.\nWarranty: Our Jolt Stun Guns are made of high-quality components and come with a lifetime warranty.\n\nCONTENTS\n\nJOLT Tactical Stun Flashlight 75,000,000*\nNylon holster\nWrist strap\nCharging Cord\nInstructions\n\n*Actual Voltage output is difficult to measure and verify, but this unit compares to other brands that claim to be 75,000,000 or more volts.', 'Tactical 75,000,000* Stun Flashlight', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tactical-75000000-stun-flashlight', '