(131, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:57', '2021-07-16 16:56:57', 'Protect yourself with the power of the Police Force\nWhether you are a law enforcement officer or the homeowner protecting your property and loved ones, the Police Force Tactical 9,000,000* Stun Baton Flashlight by Cutting Edge Products, Inc. might just be the tactical defense tool you have been looking for. Unlike rubber and plastic stun batons that are so common in the market today, this model is made of military-grade aluminum alloy so it can take (or give!) quite a beating without damaging the unit.\nThis unit is powered by a rechargeable lithium battery and combines three powerful self-defense weapons:\n Military Grade Aluminum Alloy Baton: The shockproof exterior allows it not only to be used as a self-defense tool for striking an assailant but it can withstand rugged use and extreme conditions often encountered by the military and law enforcement officers.\n\n Powerful Stun Baton: Most stun guns on the market today have only one or two points of contact. When using this model to defend yourself, the Triple Stun Technology (TST) allows an electrical charge to emanate between three separate points on the top of the stun baton (two sides and the middle). This creates a larger stun radius, allowing you to easily defend yourself. Even when test fired the loud, bright electrical burst is often enough to stop an attacker, and if not, a Jolt from this unit certainly will!\n\n Blinding 3 Watt LED with 5 Light Modes: It will not only safely illuminate the entire area at night but can also be used to protect you. When shinned in the eyes of an attacker, the ultra-bright 140 lumen light can have a temporary blinding effect making it easy for you to immobilize them with the stun gun or strike with the baton. (Note: 140 are the actual lumens. Some companies will exaggerate this number and claim a light this bright to be 280 lumens or more).\n\nAlthough this unit is designed to meet the rigorous demands of the Military and Police, it is also a great choice for civilians who want a top-quality flashlight tactical defense tool should the need arise.\nWhether you leave this stun baton by your nightstand, carry it in your car, or attach it to your belt loop, protecting yourself is as easy as 1,2,3:\n\n\nIdentify the Threat: An attacker will use the cover of darkness to sneak up on their victims and to hide their identity. He\'ll also look for the most vulnerable victim. This powerful light beam shined in the direction of a possible attacker is often enough to persuade him to go in search of an easier target.\n\nDisorient the Attacker: Shining the ultra-bright light directly into someone\'s eyes will cause disorientation and impaired vision. The Police Force 9,000,000* Metal Tactical Stun Baton Flashlight boasts a bright light beam with Self Defense Strobe that can disorient your attacker and give you time to flee.\n\n\nStrike or Stun! If these aren\'t enough to deter your attacker, a blow from the metal baton or a shock from the powerful stun gun certainly will.\n\nFEATURES\n\n\nPolice Strength Protection \nTriple Stun Technology\nTactical Striking Edge\nMilitary Grade Aluminum Alloy Body\nNonslip Grip \n3-Watt LED Flashlight\n100,000 hours Bulb Life\n5 Light Modes: LOW, MED, HIGH, STROBE, and SOS\n17\" Long\nBelt clip\nRechargeable \nSafety Switch \nEasy to Carry\nLifetime Warranty\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCONTENTS\n\nPolice Force 9,000,000* Tactical Stun Baton Flashlight\nInstructions\nWall Charger\n\n*Actual Voltage output is difficult to measure and verify, but this unit compares to other brands that claim to be 9,000,000 or more volts.', 'Tactical 9,000,000* Stun Baton Flashlight', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tactical-9000000-stun-baton-flashlight', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:57', '2021-07-16 16:56:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/tactical-9000000-stun-baton-flashlight/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(132, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:57', '2021-07-16 16:56:57', 'We now offer a Tactical Handcuff Key with a convenient clip, so you can carry it with you!\nFEATURES\n Style: The unique pen style makes it easy to wear in the pocket of your shirt or in a pair of pants.\nConvenient Clip: With the clip on the front you can attach it to your belt or shirt pocket.\nDurable: Made of aluminum alloy.\nUniversal: This handcuff key should fit most handcuffs.\nLifetime Warranty\n\nCONTENTS\nPolice Force Tactical Handcuff Key', 'Tactical Handcuff Key', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tactical-handcuff-key', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:57', '2021-07-16 16:56:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/tactical-handcuff-key/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(133, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:58', '2021-07-16 16:56:58', 'The Tactical Performance Power Magazine (PPM) is a lithium energy cell battery for the X2 or X26P CEW.\nFEATURES\n\nFits the TASER™ X2 and X26P self-defense tools\nDurable Lithium power magazine\nThe battery lasts up to 50 consecutive firings\nNon-rechargeable\nMade in the USA\n90-Day Warranty\n\nCONTENTS\nTASER™ Performance Power Magazine (PPM)', 'Tactical Performance Power Magazine (PPM)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tactical-performance-power-magazine-ppm', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:58', '2021-07-16 16:56:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/tactical-performance-power-magazine-ppm/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(134, 1, '2021-07-16 16:56:58', '2021-07-16 16:56:58', 'Used by law enforcement agencies across the country, the TCP Defense Launcher offers the most distance and power. With accuracy up to 150 ft*, when used with long-range VXR projectiles, this is a great option for those preferring the pistol form factor.\nWith a 6-round capacity, the TCP™ launches both standard round projectiles and VXR™ projectiles (sold separately), with accuracy up to 150 ft.\nFEATURES\n\nSemi-automatic\nUltra-lightweight construction\n6 round magazine capacity\nUp to 150 FT launch distance\nCompatible with both standard round projectile and VXR™ projectile (sold separately)\nCompact size fits in a holster (sold separately)\nUses both CO2 and N2 cartridges (8 Gram ONLY- not compatible with 12 Gram cartridges used in the LifeLite Launcher)\n\nSPECIFICATIONS\n\n\n\n\nLength\n8″/ 20cm\n\n\nHeight\n6.5″/ 16.5cm\n\n\nWeight\n1.71Lbs/ .77Kg\n\n\nCaliber\n.68\n\n\nAction\nSemi-auto\n\n\nPower\n8g CO2/ 1.3gN2\n\n\n\n \nCONTENTS\n\n1 Yellow TCP™ Launcher\n2 Black Universal Magazines\nManual\nSpec Sheet\n', 'TCP Defense Launcher', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tcp-defense-launcher', '', '', '2021-07-16 16:56:58', '2021-07-16 16:56:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/product/tcp-defense-launcher/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
